[iamf][Rule #5] id: assert-parameter-definition
Section 3.6.1
Parameter Definition Syntax and Semantics checks:
- There SHALL be one unique parameter_id per Parameter Substream.
- The parameter rate SHALL be a value such that the number of ticks per frame is a non-zero integer.
- duration SHALL NOT be set to 0.
- When constant_subblock_duration is equal to 0, the summation of all subblock_duration in this parameter block SHALL be equal to duration.
- subblock_duration SHALL NOT be set to 0.

